---
import StarlightPage from '@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro';
---
<StarlightPage frontmatter={{ title: 'Terms of Service', template: 'splash' }}>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Educational Purpose</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">All content on Prefrontal Profit is for educational and informational purposes only. We are a directory and comparison platform, not financial advisors.</p>
    <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Accuracy of Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">While we strive for 100% accuracy in our broker reviews and API comparisons, brokerage terms change frequently. Users should verify details on the broker's official site.</p>
    <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Risk Disclosure</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Trading in equities and derivatives involves significant risk. Prefrontal Profit is not liable for any financial losses incurred through the use of tools or brokers listed on this site.</p>
  </div>
</StarlightPage>